flowchart LR
  U[User/Role] --> I[IdP/SSO]
  I --> P[Policy Engine: RBAC/ABAC]
  P --> Q[Query Request + User Context]
  Q --> F[Permission Filter / Metadata Filter]
  F --> V[(Vector DB)]
  V --> C[Context Guard / 二次检查]
  C --> L[LLM NIM]
  L --> G[Prompt Injection Guard]
  G --> A[Answer with Citations or Refusal]
  C -.access records.-> AU[Audit Log]
  G -.output records.-> AU
